description:
multipart.NextPart: No newline after the last boundary.

File uloads from Adobe's air on mobile platforms do not have a trailing newline.
multipart.NextPart looks for a trailing newline. If there is none all the form
parts are removed and an error is returned.

This patch is ok with no trailing newline.
subject: multipart.NextPart: No newline after the last boundary.
